Entry Price (EP):  When someone calls for a stock  that person must have a vested interest.  So definitely he/ she will enter at the price which he has pre-determined.  Just like going to a restaurant to eat  before recommending anyone  you would have tried the food yourself. But whether you yourself want to try the food in the restaurant based on the recommendation  no one can force youTarget Price (TP):  How much you want to eat in the restaurant  half full  not full or full full is entirely up to youStop loss (SL):  The food in the restaurant is not nice  you have to decide if want to continue to eat  to throw away  or continue to eat till you vomit.  But you cannot ask for refund as it is the choice you have made for yourself
